  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个数据交换的时序图，描述消费者和提供者之间如何完成数据合约和传输。核心角色有四个：ConsumerBackend、ConsumerConnector、ProviderConnector、ProviderBackend。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerBackend",
        "ConsumerConnector",
        "ProviderConnector",
        "ProviderBackend"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，四个参与者已经排好顺序。那交互流程从哪里开始？是ConsumerConnector主动发起吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerConnector"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，ConsumerConnector先向ProviderConnector查询可用的数据产品，就是query data offers，然后ProviderConnector返回metadata。接着ConsumerConnector发起合约请求contract request，对方返回contract agreement。之后ConsumerConnector请求具体的artifact，ProviderConnector返回access information。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerConnector",
        "ProviderConnector",
        "query data offers",
        "return metadata",
        "contract request",
        "contract agreement",
        "request artifact",
        "return access information"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，前面六条消息已经画好了。接下来是实际的数据传输部分吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerConnector",
        "ProviderConnector"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，这里有个分支逻辑。数据拉取有两种协议：PULL和PUSH。如果是PULL模式，ConsumerBackend直接向ProviderBackend请求数据，然后返回数据；如果是PUSH模式，则是ProviderBackend主动把数据推给ConsumerBackend，ConsumerBackend自己处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerBackend",
        "ProviderBackend",
        "protocol.PULL",
        "protocol.PUSH",
        "request data",
        "return data",
        "push data",
        "process data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，alt分支里的PULL和else分支里的PUSH是互斥的吗？还有PUSH模式下ConsumerBackend那条自环消息process data是表示内部处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "alt",
        "else",
        "ConsumerBackend",
        "process data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，两种协议二选一。PUSH模式下ConsumerBackend收到数据后需要本地处理，所以画个自环表示内部处理流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "protocol.PULL",
        "protocol.PUSH",
        "ConsumerBackend",
        "process data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。整个流程从Connector层的发现和合约协商，到底层的两种数据传输模式都画清楚了。你看还有什么需要调整的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerConnector",
        "ProviderConnector",
        "ConsumerBackend",
